13","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe people will be assembled barefoot, naked, and uncircumcised.\u201d I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, will the men and women look at each other?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThe matter will be too serious for them to notice.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1092,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/11\/06\/play-sign-eid\/","url_meta":{"origin":10921,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Eid: Let them play and sing on Eid","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 6, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: Abu Bakr came to her on the day of\u00a0Eid\u00a0while the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, was with her and there were two girls singing songs of the Ansar\u00a0on the day of Bu'ath. Abu Bakr said twice, \"Musical instruments of Satan!\" The Prophet said, \"Leave them Abu\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":9733,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/09\/qiblah-woman-salat-dogs\/","url_meta":{"origin":10921,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Prayer: Does a woman invalidate a man&#8217;s prayer?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 9, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: That which invalidates prayer was mentioned in her presence and they said, \u201cPrayer is invalidated by a dog, a donkey, and a woman.\u201d Aisha said, \u201cYou have turned us into dogs! I have seen the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, praying while I was between him\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/10921","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=10921"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/10921\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=10921"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=10921"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=10921"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}